        fiscal year-end; quarterly reporters appear in all six periods. Minimum n = 4 per region per period.
      </p>

      <!-- SVG: regional median trajectories -->
      <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2">Median RG10 by Region</h3>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
